description: I've been dreaming about how things would be if one of my models had a twin. What would it be like to shoot a scene with identical twin brothers? That fantasy of mine, through advances in technology, I can now make a reality. It is with great pleasure that I bring you Maskurbate's first twins' contest, Ricky vs Ricky. The rules are simple, the first one who cums wins. Who will win and how? Which one is the more confident? Which one has the bigger dick? Let's find out!
title: Twins' Contest - Ricky vs Ricky, Scene #01
